<span class="PRTitle"><!-- NewsTitle.start -->TRANSCRIPT OF INTERVIEW WITH SENATOR JUAN MIGUEL ZUBIRI<!-- NewsTitle.end --></span>
<br /><span class="PRSub"><!-- NewsTitleSub.start -->Vice-Chair Senate Committee on Local Government<!-- NewsTitleSub.end--></span>
